<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Page Not Found - 404 Error</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #2b6095; /* Light gray background color */
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px; /* Increased container width */
      padding: 60px; /* Increased padding */
      background-color: #ffffff; /* White background color */
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      text-align: center;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 36px; /* Larger font size for the heading */
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #FF4136;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 20px; /* Larger font size for the content */
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #333;
    }

    .error-icon {
      font-size: 64px; /* Larger icon */
      color: #FF4136;
      margin-bottom: 30px; /* Increased margin */
    }

    .back-button a {
      padding: 15px 30px; /* Larger button padding */
      background-color: #007BFF;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
      font-size: 20px; /* Larger button font size */
    }

    .back-button a:hover {
      background-color: #0056b3;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle error-icon"></i>
    <h1>404 - Page Not Found</h1>
    <p>The page you are looking for might have been removed, had its name changed, or is temporarily unavailable.</p>
    <div class="back-button">
      <a href="/">Back to Homepage</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Font Awesome (for the error icon) -->
  <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/a076d05399.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
